column5: Can you name last year's 2nd place finisher's at the 2nd Sucks tournament on Rice Lake?     The honour of cleaning donated walleye for everyone's dinner is awarded to the 2nd place team.  1st is great, third is nice but 2nd SUCKS.
Well I know Ron is one of them
Yeah and his partner seems to be pulling his weight too. Standing around while Ron gets the job done.
I know one just got a nice musky on a Handlebarz and is very happy looks about the same as in that pic
It is a five fish limit. Bass & walleye combo. Most walleye weighed in get donated for the dinner but trust me the dinner alone is worth fishing this event. Great time had by all.
That be Mr Giles and Mr. Reynes.  Sounds like fun, like to fish it this year and see Rons fillet skills in person for a second time.

Gee thanks for posting that Mike.... Your a great friend..... NOT!  Hey it was all in great fun. I now understand why people claim to say they don't know how to fillet fish though. You gonna make it out Phil?   Cheers, Ron...
The date is September 30th. Give Ben a call for more info. He can be reached at 905 797-2632
I am working on it as we speak Ron, have a couple feelers out.  Have to better the odds of you filleting again somehow!
Thanks Ron. Is that Ben from BJ's?
